https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=23939	32940
精力充沛的双胞胎Frederik和Gerrit Braun不乏梦想，他们用了7年时间花了480万美元，建造了世界上最大的机场模型“<a href="http://www.miniatur-wunderland.com/exhibit/multimedia/foto/galerie/airport/airport-terminal/">Knuffingen Airport</a>(<a href="http://www.miniatur-wunderland.com/exhibit/video/miwula-tv/film/article/launch-of-the-knuffingen-airport/">视频</a>)”。<i>
